{"tid":1431822,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"FB地區page 乜乜友 背後組織資料！！","createTime":"2019-08-08T05:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T06:39:06.000Z","uid":109820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0a47ef664958b31665ad31fd70e4d49d8c778c8b","tid":1431822,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:35:39.000Z","msg":"（借朋友acc post）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大大力推</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係紅色資本滲透後生仔嘅其中一條路徑，不過係幾年前嘅，知情人士可以補充：<br />\n<br />\n咁其實想講兩間機構<br />\n<strong>大中華青年在線</strong>（前揸fit人：劉迺強）<br />\n<strong>新青年論壇</strong>（揸fit人：<span style=\"color: red;\">四川省政协港区委员及观塘区区议员<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">邓咏骏</span></span>）<br />\n兩間機構係有啲似兄弟關係，入面嘅人都成日share 黎用嘅。<br />\n******************************<br />\n咁<strong>大中華</strong>就主要搞一啲同中國有關嘅中學生活動，例如去世博、四川、內蒙等等，仲有搞下啲基本法講座、<strong>中史通識網</strong>咁。<br />\n如果啲後生仔女表現得好，就會拉攏佢地加入幫手，甚至帶去<strong>新青年</strong>度。<br />\n<br />\n至於搞中史通識網，可以俾佢地輕易透過&quot;知識&quot;控制班學生嘅思想，呢單野好嚴重！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">e+史識 <a href=\"http://www.eltp-ch.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eltp-ch.com%2F&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rBvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=608757ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.eltp-ch.com/</a><br />\n仲請緊人，今日截止： <a href=\"https://www.recruit.com.hk/m/JobDetail.aspx?jobId=L0478062\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.recruit.com.hk%2Fm%2FJobDetail.aspx%3FjobId%3DL0478062&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rBvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=ea58e82e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.recruit.com.hk/m/JobDetail.aspx?jobId=L0478062</a></span><br />\n<br />\n另外可能無咩人知嘅係，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>D18、18區&quot;xxx友&quot;呢啲facebook page（e.g. 沙田友）</strong></span>其實係佢地搵後生仔搞，每人負責一兩個page，出一條post就幾蚊咁。<br />\n<br />\n仲有<span style=\"color: red;\">時聞香港</span>都同佢地有關。<br />\n******************************<br />\n而<strong>新青年論壇</strong>就咗廿幾年兩岸四地大專生交流團-<span style=\"color: red;\">龍願</span>，如果表現得好，就搵你幫手做籌委，再熟啲就搵你<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">入黨</span></span>：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20120908/18010902\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120908%2F18010902&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rBvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=2bdc4056\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120908%2F18010902&h=87dc4a0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20120908/18010902</a><br />\n個交流團係連<strong>台灣澳門</strong>都搞埋嘅，所以其實佢地會唔會係呢啲時候物色當地人做老共枝針+宣揚中國嘅思想？自己諗。<br />\n<br />\n另外補充少少，兩間野都有好多人黎自香島中學。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後，差唔多開學啦，無論老師定學生，參加活動時記得Check清楚個背景，唔好一個唔覺意就主動送中。</span>"},{"pid":"0d59cff1d5f5f38d6448b0bb193583487104b2bb","tid":1431822,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:36:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff9828dad110addbd406a6f669a1123276f5345e","tid":1431822,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今朝開post可能揀錯分台所以無咩人理<br />\n麻煩大家推一推！"},{"pid":"1e750a95ac474f1b0db5b86467954e667ba5ab24","tid":1431822,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:48:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c465547b52314019ea30498a6a92c42b41e8f258","tid":1431822,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:48:22.000Z","msg":"自推到有人理！"},{"pid":"cef66bb96b6f033f3fabbe14a7ae2d9bc5589c63","tid":1431822,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4457b289a0bc23a39678aee60dca01bdb3d3fe18","tid":1431822,"uid":109820,"